<A HREF="quests.php3"><B>Quests:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
I posted the complete spoiler for the Magician's Epic Weapon. While this quest has not been solved yet (to my knowledge), it seems that all the elements and sub-quests have been completed since they fixed some things in the last patch. I expect someone to finally get the reward, probably tonight, so as soon as that happens I will update the quest to reflect it.
</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">1. <A HREF="quest_detail.php3?search=475">Magician's Class Weapon Quest</A></FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="items.phtml"><B>Items:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
