<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">1. <A HREF="weapon_detail.php3?search=479">Swiftwind</A> - One of the Ranger Epic weapons.</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">2. <A HREF="weapon_detail.php3?search=480">Earthcaller</A> - One of the Ranger Epic weapons.</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">3. <A HREF="weapon_detail.php3?search=481">Fiery Defender</A> - Paladin's Epic weapon.</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">4. <A HREF="weapon_detail.php3?search=482">Nature's Walker Scimitar</A> - Druid Epic weapon.</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">5. <A HREF="armor_detail.php3?search=879">Celestial Fists</A> - Monk's Epic armor.</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">6. <A HREF="weapon_detail.php3?search=483">Innoruuk's Curse</A> - Shadowknights Epic weapon.</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">7. <A HREF="weapon_detail.php3?search=484">Staff of the Four</A> - Wizard's Epic weapon.</FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="main.phtml"><B>Polls:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
Here are the results of the poll <I></I>"Will you be buying the Scars of Velious expansion pack next month?"</I>. This expansion is due to be released tomorrow. 539 people responded with the overwhelming majority saying they will be buying the expansion, indicating that EQ is still going strong and will continue to do so for a while yet!</FONT><BR><BR>

